isches Verständnis der Mittelalter-Germanistik. Mit einem Nachwort von Racha Kirakosian.  afunded by VolkswagenStiftung  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aLiteratur. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aMediävistik. 4aMittelalter. 4aMittelalterrezeption. 4aRoman. 4aRomantik. 4aWissenschaft. 4aWissenschaftsgeschichte. 4aÜbersetzung. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  aCultural History.  aHistory of Science.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.  aMedieval Studies.  aMiddle Age.  aNovel.  aRomanticism.  aScience.  aTranslation.1 aKirakosian, Racha, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPerplies, Helge, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut2 aVolkswagenStiftungefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2023z9783111024950oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839468920?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839468920423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839468920/original  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-TGPb2023